events.name: Startup Grind
events.description: Apr. 11-12—Global 2023 will bring together the world's leading founders, investors, and mentors to tackle the core challenges every startup faces: fundraising, sales, marketing, and product. Join us and thousands of early-stage startup teams to learn, grow and connect.

events.name: DeveloperWeek 2023
events.description: DeveloperWeek Europe 2023 is the largest virtual software developer conference & expo dedicated to Europe's tech community. Come join 2,000+ engineering professionals and technical practitioners & leaders from across Europe as the community gathers for two days of education & networking.

events.name: JSHeroes
events.description: May 18 to 19—JSHeroes is a non-profit community-organized conference, held every year in Cluj, Romania. Our goal is to bring together JS and Web/Frontend development enthusiasts from all over the world, for a 2-day event with: great talks, amazing networking and tons of fun.

heading_learning.title: Darbuotojų apmokymai

heading_events.title: Registracija į renginius
heading_events.description: Čia galite matyti ateityje vyksiančius renginius. Norėdami aplikuoti ir gauti finansavimą, aplikuokite į renginį - bus nusiųstas prašymas jūsų vadovui. Dėl kilusių klausimų kreipkitės į Vardenis Pavardenis.
